    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Thanks for y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                    <unclear reason="illegible">four</unclear> kind letters &amp; for <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0639">the confession of
                    Wattâ€™s</title></bibl>. it is certainly undeniable proof of the design of a
                    rising. I trust the ugly business in <placeName ref="pl0229">Glasgow</placeName>
                    will soon be at an end.</p>
                <p>My best thanks to <persName ref="pe0198">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Ker</persName>. for his kind intentions. To y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>self for what you can say more about <persName ref="pe0184">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Bell</persName>.</p>
                <p>If franks are to be abolished we must write on a single sheet.</p>
                <p>I beg my compliments to <persName ref="pe0001">Doctor Anderson</persName> I never
                    got his <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0137">work on foreign
                        sheep</title></bibl> which he promised to send to <persName ref="pe0026">Mess<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> White</persName>. I sent their for
                        <persName ref="pe0001">the doctor</persName> the odd sheets.</p>
                <closer><salute>Adieu D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir <lb/>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> most truly</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">TP</persName></signed>.
                <dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> Dec<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        18<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1794.</dateline></closer>

                <postscript>
                    <p>If by return of post. you will send me the event of the <placeName ref="pl0229">Glasgow</placeName> affair you will ease my mind you may
                        inclose till parlement meets.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
